WEBVTT

00:01.083 --> 00:04.719
<i>And it's the annual Boston Police
Department salute to heroes tonight.</i>

00:04.885 --> 00:07.664
<i>Boston homicide detective
Jane Rizzoli,</i>

00:07.830 --> 00:10.427
<i>who was badly injured in a siege
at headquarters three months ago,</i>

00:10.593 --> 00:11.680
<i>will be honored,</i>

00:11.805 --> 00:14.598
<i>along with army private Abby Sherman,
just 22 years old.</i>

00:15.060 --> 00:17.267
<i>Sherman's story made headlines
when her platoon</i>

00:17.433 --> 00:19.269
<i>was ambushed in Afghanistan.</i>

00:19.435 --> 00:23.065
<i>She was shot but crawled to a machine gun
to save three members of her squad.</i>

